<!doctype html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta name="layout" content="main"/>
    <title>Welcome to Booking tool</title>
</head>
<body>

<div class="svg" role="presentation">
    <div class="booking-logo-container">
        <a class="navbar-brand" href="/#">
            <asset:image src="booking-logo-white.svg" class="booking-logo"/>
        </a>
    </div>
</div>
<div id="content" role="main">
    <section class="row colset-2-its">
        <h1>Actual Features</h1>
        <div id="controllers" role="navigation">
        <ul>
            <li>You can only use one user for a limited time, if someone else is using it you must wait a specified time to 5 min. But this is not always true.</li>
            <li>You must select in which ODC you want to make the reservation for a room</li>
            <li>There is a time of approximately 5 min to make the reservation, otherwise the program closes the session, without further notice</li>
            <li>You can select in the form to reserve the room: Eagle Id, Name, LOB, Day, Room, Start time, start minute, end hour, end minute</li>
        </ul>
        <br>
        <asset:image src="booking-temp-3.jpeg" class="booking-logo"/>
        <asset:image src="booking-temp-4.jpeg" class="booking-logo"/>
    </section>
    <section class="row colset-2-its">
        <h1>Proposal</h1>
        <h2>Proposal Features</h2>
        <div id="controllers" role="navigation">
        <ul>
            <li>Service provided to multiple users at the same time (availability).
            <li>Implementing SQL DB.</li>
            <li>One month of booking</li>
            <li>Booking for multiple day at a time</li>
            <li>Improvement of ui</li>
            <li>Log In</li>
            <li>Admin registration table</li>
            <li>Implementation of maintainable Code</li>
            <li>Front end and back end implementation</li>
            <li>Documentation</li>
        </ul>
        <br>
        <h2>Proposal Technologies</h2>
        <div id="controllers" role="navigation">
        <ul>
            <li>Groovy & Grails. (Back-Front)</li>
            <li>SQL-Lite. (DataBase)</li>
        </ul>
        <br>
        <h2>Proposal Server</h2>
        <div id="controllers" role="navigation">
        <ul>
            <li>Windows PC computer</li>
            <li>Allowed in the ODC</li>
            <li>Exposition of port (80 or 443 [Certificate])</li>
            <li>With Java version 1.80.222 installed</li>
        </ul>
        <br>
        <asset:image src="booking-temp-1.jpeg" class="booking-logo"/>
        <asset:image src="booking-temp-2.jpeg" class="booking-logo"/>
    </section>
</div>
